<i>Will Corinne ever forgive</i>
<i>Jessica and Chester</i>

23:15.640 --> 23:17.632
<i>for not telling her</i>
<i>she was adopted?</i>

23:17.840 --> 23:20.639
<i>Will the court accept</i>
<i>Burt's findings as evidence,</i>

23:20.840 --> 23:23.435
<i>or will the judge rule it "hair-say"?</i>

23:23.640 --> 23:25.950
<i>Did Jessica kill Peter Campbell,</i>

23:26.160 --> 23:28.880
<i>or does she merely</i>
<i>collect murder weapons?</i>

23:29.080 --> 23:33.438
<i>Will the Tates do without dessert,</i>
<i>or will they eat Heinrich's pants?</i>

23:33.640 --> 23:35.996
<i>These questions and many others</i>
<i>will be answered</i>

23:36.200 --> 23:39.034
<i>on next week's episode of</i> Soap.

